Here you will find best practice guidance and design solutions for specific user
tasks and scenarios.

Some of the patterns in this section contain coded examples, others are written
guidance. Patterns often use single or combinations of components and describe
their use in context of their relationship to the user.

On the most part, if you are using the [GOV.UK Prototype Kit](https://govuk-prototype-kit-beta.herokuapp.com) or
have [GOV.UK Frontend](https://github.com/alphagov/govuk-frontend)
included in your build, the coded examples provided should render exactly as
they do inside the design system.
